c: 40
v: 43
t: "hqana 'ana ma tadeunani 'iilaa alaietiqad bih la yastahiqu aldaewat 'ilyh, wala yulja 'iilayh fi aldunya wala fi alakhirat lejzh wnqsh, waelamuu 'ana masir alkhlayq klha 'iilaa allah sbhanh, wahu yjazy kl eamil bemlh, wa'ana aladhin teddu hududah balmeasy wsfk aldima' walkfr hum 'ahl alnar"